rance%2Ftheatres.jpg&h=752ca623&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nPo都po張一戰啦..."},{"pid":"4cbde7273e8a2075871585a60313db22e279c499","tid":464080,"uid":27935,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T23:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67ea5a83d4bca058ca04bfb269b212640250ff85","tid":464080,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T23:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加拿大國會大廈陣亡將士紀念堂<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.spiritofcanada.com/veterans/news/pastEvents/bookRemembrance/theatres.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiritofcanada.com%2Fveterans%2Fnews%2FpastEvents%2FbookRemembrance%2Ftheatres.jpg&h=752ca623&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nPo都po張一戰啦...</blockquote><br />\nRemembrance Day去到今時今日係一齊紀念一、二次世界大戰陣亡將士<br />\n就算係Montreal嘅和平紀念碑都係刻咗兩次世界大戰嘅年份<br />\n我間大學亦有石碑刻印住大戰期間陣亡嘅學生"},{"pid":"1b8b70119bb0459811f2295c802a8f0d3e5590f5","tid":464080,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T23:59:42.000Z","msg":"支那人冷血<br />\n白事變紅事做<br />\n<br />\n你第一日知?"},{"pid":"7433068bbe98896ed2c663844ef44fa289393d8c","tid":464080,"uid":12367,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T00:27:10.000Z","msg":"尋日買左好多...<br />\n一起身仲以為有..<br />\n原來已經過左1111😭"},{"pid":"c22d569f894929e9bb17e6cee80dee16cac0582e","tid":464080,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T00:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da3a650e0ffdebd0069b99d259aea3a8730847f5","tid":464080,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T00:29:23.000Z","msg":"香港保衛戰都唔撚記得？<br />\n支那畜幫過香港啲咩？"},{"pid":"8036fd2d79d254e9d6d9c14bc79421d8f7d76fcb","tid":464080,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T00:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日買左好多...<br />\n一起身仲以為有..<br />\n原來已經過左1111😭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/085320_ea3d